                            <comment id="13029301" author="mikep" created="Thu, 5 May 2011 12:32:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FYI, as a workaround i now use:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;@Component
@SlingServlet(
        generateComponent = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;,
        paths = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/my/cool/path&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13029310" author="cziegeler" created="Thu, 5 May 2011 12:57:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I agree - this is a bug&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll add the parameters for metatype, name, label, and description like we have for SlingFilter and metatype will default to false&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13029312" author="cziegeler" created="Thu, 5 May 2011 13:03:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in revision 1099777&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13029314" author="mikep" created="Thu, 5 May 2011 13:04:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Cool, thanks! &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I just saw another thing which might be related: SlingServletComponentTag tries to set immediate to true (unless i&apos;m misunderstanding something), but currently this is not applied and the components are still registered as delayed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13029316" author="mikep" created="Thu, 5 May 2011 13:08:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Never mind my previous comment, it coincided with your checkin of the fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
